<h2 id="donald-normans-model">Donald Normanâ€™s model</h2>

<ul>
  <li>
    <p>Seven stages</p>

    <ol>
      <li>
        <p>user establishes the goal</p>
      </li>
      <li>formulates intention</li>
      <li>specifies actions at interface</li>
      <li>executes action</li>
      <li>perceives system state</li>
      <li>interprets system state</li>
      <li>evaluates system state with respect to goal</li>
    </ol>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Normanâ€™s model concentrates on userâ€™s view of the interface</p>
  </li>
</ul>

<p><br /></p>

<h2 id="executionevaluation-loop">Execution/evaluation loop</h2>

<p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/speardragon/save-image-repo/main/img/image-20220909223702146.png" alt="image-20220909223702146" /></p>

