<h2 id="using-normans-model">Using Normanâ€™s model</h2>

<ul>
  <li>Some systems are harder to use than others</li>
  <li>Gulf of Execution
    <ul>
      <li>Gap btw: userâ€™s formulation of actions â‰  actions allowed by the system</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>Gulf of Evaluation
    <ul>
      <li>Gap btw: userâ€™s expectation of changed system state â‰  actual presentation of this state</li>
      <li>ì‹¤ì œì™€ ìœ ì €ê°€ ìƒê°í–ˆë˜ ê²ƒê³¼ ë‹¤ë¥¼ ë•Œ</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>Gulf of Execution Example: VCR problem</li>
</ul>

<p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/speardragon/save-image-repo/main/img/image-20220909223815585.png" alt="image-20220909223815585" /></p>

