<h2 id="form-fills">Form-fills</h2>

<p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/speardragon/save-image-repo/main/img/image-20220909224429864.png" alt="image-20220909224429864" /></p>

<ul>
  <li>Primarily for data entry or data retrieval</li>
  <li>Screen like paper form.</li>
  <li>Data put in relevant place</li>
  <li>Requires
    <ul>
      <li>good design</li>
      <li>obvious correction facilities</li>
