<h2 id="spreadsheets">Spreadsheets</h2>

<ul>
  <li>first spreadsheet VisiCalc, followed by Lotus 1-2-3, MS Excel most common today</li>
  <li>sophisticated variation of form-filling.
    <ul>
      <li><strong>grid of cells</strong> contain a value or a formula</li>
      <li>formula can involve values of other cells
        <ul>
          <li>e.g. sum of all cells in this column</li>
        </ul>
      </li>
      <li>user can enter and alter data spreadsheet maintains consistency</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
</ul>

